data.description: Newly renovated 4-bedroom home near shopping and schools. The spacious living room has high ceilings, a fireplace and plenty of windows for natural light. tile floor, quartz countertops and plenty of storage with a large pantry complement the kitchen. The first floor is completed with a 4TH BEDROOM, separate laundry room and 3full baths with a shower. Upstairs, the primary bedroom has an attached private bath with plenty of space for clothes in the adjacent walk-in closet. Views of the Sunrise golf course! waiting for you both the 2nd and 3rd second floor bedrooms. Besides a two-car garage, there are bonus storage areas under the stairs and in the second upstairs bathroom. You will find a fully fenced backyard just waiting for your personal touches.
